When trying to use Liveview the device is unable to connect to the Liveview server. 

*Test Steps:*
# Create an alloy application
# Enable liveview 
# Run application to device 

*Expected result*
Device should be able to connect to the liveview server and be able to make changes.

*Actual result* 
